					          31 U.S.C.9303
				        ) and Treasury Department CircularNo.154 dated July1,1978 (31 CFR Part225)). In addition, a duly executed power of attorney and agreement authorizing the collection or sale of such United States bonds or notes in the event of default of the principal on the bond shall accompany the deposited bonds or notes. The contracting officer may-
